(18781, 14471, 0, 1, 'Terrify (demo)', '', '2011-04-10 00:00:00', 0000, 0, 2, 7, 'Terrify\r\n\r\n(verse)\r\nYou know I am not a lady               \r\nI never wear stupid dress \r\nPatient, tender is not my nature\r\nSorry sorry I am not your ending \r\n\r\nThey say I am not a lier  \r\nCause I always have my own opinions\r\nToady, flatter is not my favor \r\nMaybe maybe I just too lazy\r\n \r\n(pre-chorus)\r\nLofty goddess,\r\neveryone want get closer\r\nFallen ethic, \r\nall the man have no difference\r\n\r\n(chorus)\r\nDo you know your deeds is terrify\r\nDon''t you know I never satisfy\r\nIt is your will jump into the cave \r\nIn the end don''t blam me didn''t say\r\n\r\n(verse2)\r\nYou know I am not your candy\r\nI never pretend obedient\r\nLoyal promise is not my answer\r\nSorry sorry too much apologize\r\n\r\nThey say I should learn to cherish  \r\nBut I think your longing is incurable\r\nNo one will agree with me \r\nMaybe maybe I am go crazy ', '', 280, '', '李方', '李方', '', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2009-08-27 04:52:26', '2015-03-12 13:40:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
